---
applyTo: '**'
description: RemoteEvent standards
alwaysApply: true
---

Networking Rules:

Use RemoteEvents by default.

Use RemoteFunctions only when synchronous response is required.

All remotes must live under:

ReplicatedStorage.Remotes

Structure:

Remotes
    Events
    Functions

Naming:

AttackEvent
PurchaseItemEvent
EquipWeaponEvent

Never:

DoStuff
Action
Test

Pattern:

Client
    ->
RemoteEvent
    ->
Controller
    ->
Service

Never execute game logic directly from a remote.